headline: Seagate Technology (STX) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of data storage manufacturer Seagate (NASDAQ:STX) jumped 3.4% in the afternoon session after Bernstein SocGen Group raised its price target on the stock, citing accelerating demand for data storage driven by the AI boom. The firm increased its price target to $275 from $250 while keeping an "Outperform" rating.
